body:
When I try to start the vagrant setup from master I get the following errors and Kubernetes does't start (I'm on OSX)

``` bash
$ sudo journalctl -u kubelet
....
Apr 20 14:31:44 kubernetes-master kubelet[4719]: E0420 14:31:44.714089    4719 pod_workers.go:138] Error syncing pod 31157f482aa8557a2a744911683a3972, skipping: failed to "StartContainer" for "POD" with ImageInspectError: "Failed to inspect image \"gcr.io/google_containers/pause:2.0\": json: cannot unmarshal number into Go value of type string"
Apr 20 14:31:49 kubernetes-master kubelet[4719]: I0420 14:31:49.687209    4719 manager.go:1723] Need to restart pod infra container for "kube-scheduler-kubernetes-master_kube-system(b11f6ca51ffdd7eb4482e71254a8fc13)" because it is not found
Apr 20 14:31:49 kubernetes-master kubelet[4719]: I0420 14:31:49.688067    4719 manager.go:1723] Need to restart pod infra container for "kube-controller-manager-kubernetes-master_kube-system(6eff975d4eccf1bb27ad09408bc54172)" because it is not found
Apr 20 14:31:49 kubernetes-master kubelet[4719]: E0420 14:31:49.701465    4719 manager.go:1893] Failed to create pod infra container: ImageInspectError; Skipping pod "kube-controller-manager-kubernetes-master_kube-system(6eff975d4eccf1bb27ad09408bc54172)"
Apr 20 14:31:49 kubernetes-master kubelet[4719]: E0420 14:31:49.701515    4719 pod_workers.go:138] Error syncing pod 6eff975d4eccf1bb27ad09408bc54172, skipping: failed to "StartContainer" for "POD" with ImageInspectError: "Failed to inspect image \"gcr.io/google_containers/pause:2.0\": json: cannot unmarshal number into Go value of type string"
Apr 20 14:31:49 kubernetes-master kubelet[4719]: E0420 14:31:49.712017    4719 manager.go:1893] Failed to create pod infra container: ImageInspectError; Skipping pod "kube-scheduler-kubernetes-master_kube-system(b11f6ca51ffdd7eb4482e71254a8fc13)"
Apr 20 14:31:49 kubernetes-master kubelet[4719]: E0420 14:31:49.712053    4719 pod_workers.go:138] Error syncing pod b11f6ca51ffdd7eb4482e71254a8fc13, skipping: failed to "StartContainer" for "POD" with ImageInspectError: "Failed to inspect image \"gcr.io/google_containers/pause:2.0\": json: cannot unmarshal number into Go value of type string"
```

Docker allready loaded the image but it doesn't get started:

``` bash
[vagrant@kubernetes-master ~]$ sudo docker ps -a

```

And Kubernetes of course isn't available:

``` bash
$ ./cluster/kubectl.sh cluster-info                                                                                                                                          
The connection to the server 10.245.1.2 was refused - did you specify the right host or port?
```

I built my own binaries and wanted to test them (build ran successfully) but the cluster doesn't come up. Do you know what the problem is? Running `./cluster/kube-push.sh` didn't solved the problem either.

Thanks for your help!
title: Vagrant - Error start up cluster
